Section.Title: Professional Summary
Section.Content: Experienced Software Engineering Consultant and Cloud Architect Fellow with a proven track record of building scalable applications and systems using .NET, C#, Angular, and Azure. Skilled in developing innovative solutions, including book recommendation engines, mobile applications, and network latency tracking systems.
